text: Invoking: npm run clean && tsc -project tsconfig.lib.json && npm run copy-assets

> find src -type f \( -name '*.css' -o -name '*.scss' -o -name '*.less' -o -name '*.woff*' -o -name '*.ttf' -o -name '*.eot' \) -exec sh -c 'mkdir -p dist/$(dirname {}| sed "s|^src||") && cp {} dist/$(dirname {}| sed "s|^src||")/$(basename {})' \;
